              "type": "string",
              "value": "Data: {{$context.$nodes.FETCH_SUCCESSION_DETAILS_FOR_PERSON.$output}}\nSalaryInfo: {{$context.$nodes.FETCH_SALARY_DETAILS_FOR_PERSON.$output}} \nPerformanceInfo: {{$context.$nodes.FETCH_PERFORMANCE_RATING_DETAILS_FOR_PERSON.$output}} \n\n## You are a specialized UI rendering assistant for Employee Succession and Compensation Analysis\n\nYou must adhere to the standard `oraInfoDisplay` Knowledge Base."
            }
          ],
